message: "If you use this software, please cite it as below."
title: "givp: GRASP-ILS-VND with Path Relinking"
abstract: >
  A direction-agnostic metaheuristic optimizer combining GRASP construction,
  Iterated Local Search (ILS), Variable Neighborhood Descent (VND) and
  bidirectional Path Relinking for continuous, integer and mixed-variable
  problems.
type: software
authors:
